    Record5	    Value3
    Record6	    Value3
    Record7	    Value4
    Record8	    Value5
    Record9	    Value5
    Record10	Value5
    Record11	Value6
    Record12	Value7
    Record13	Value7
    Record14	Value7
    Record15	Value8
    Record16	Value9
    Record17	Value10
    Record18	Value10
    Record19	Value10
    Record20	Value10

Then do running the following code:

